These are programs that I run that work with the anvil local webserver. I run them as services when the Raspberry Pi boots up. All of the files are in the services directory.

Services

/etc/systemd/system

mystartup.service - Uses /usr/local/bin/start_led.sh

shutdown-script.service - Uses /home/frank/anvildir/M3_App_2/services/shutdown.py

start_anvil_check.service - Uses /usr/local/bin/start_anvil_check.sh

User Service

/home/frank/.config/systemd/user

mystartup2.service - Uses /home/frank/.config/systemd/user/start_anvil.sh

